OL,5, One of the UK's biggest energy         
OL,6, suppliers has warned that up to 40% of 
OL,7, its customers will be in fuel poverty  
OL,8, by October as it called on the         
OL,9, government to help struggling homes.   
OL,11,FE.On UK boss Michael Lewis said the    
OL,12,Frise in energy prices is               
OL,13,F"unprecedented" and a growing number of
OL,14,Fits customers are in arrears.          
OL,16,FThe government is facing calls to levy 
OL,17,Fa windfall tax on oil and gas firms.   
OL,19,FEducation Secretary Nadhim Zahawi said 
OL,20,FRishi Sunak will look at all options.  
